This paper discusses the performance of packet aggregation in IEEE 802.11ac MU-MIMO WLANs, which is related to network protocols and wireless communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory and signal processing, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper discusses system performance, which is related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and security, which is related to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
